      "description": "This 996-generation 911 Carrera delivers a visceral, analog driving experience centered around its 3.4L naturally aspirated flat-six powerplant. The engine features a smooth power band and has been proactively maintained with a ceramic IMS bearing retrofit and a fresh rear main seal. Power is sent to the rear wheels via a precise G96 6-speed manual transaxle. The suspension geometry is sharpened by Bilstein B8 dampers, providing excellent lateral stability and damping control. Braking performance is handled by Brembo-sourced four-piston monobloc calipers over vented rotors, ensuring consistent pedal feel. With its hydraulic steering rack offering superb tactile feedback and a chassis free of subframe corrosion, this example is a mechanically sound driver\u2019s car optimized for spirited performance.",
